{"article_id":"h9DKEyxs62jFwLQ8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Speaker John A. Boehner on Wednesday dared President Obama to veto the Republican \" Plan B \" offer","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to avoid the \" fiscal cliff \"","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"- higher tax rates on those","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"making more than $ 1 million","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"but tax cuts for everyone else -","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"even as the president pleaded for cooperation rather than confrontation ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"he has already moved halfway .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The high-stakes game of chicken between the country ' s top Republican and top Democrat comes with less than two weeks to go before the fiscal cliff , a quick succession of across-the-board tax increases and $ 110 billion in spending cuts","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"that strike at the beginning of the new year .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"Seeking to add some political leverage to a weak hand ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Mr. Boehner will have the House vote Thursday on his Plan B ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"and he said","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"he expects to have the votes","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to pass it","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"despite a revolt among his conservative members .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"After that ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"he said ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"it will be Mr. Obama ' s problem .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"\" The president will have a decision to make .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"He can call on the Senate Democrats","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"to pass our bill","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"or he can be responsible for the largest tax increase in American history , \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Mr. Boehner said in a 50-second news conference","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"where he took no questions .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"White House aides earlier in the day had already said","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Mr. Obama will veto the bill","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"should it reach his desk .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"And in his own impromptu news conference ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"where he did take questions ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. Obama said","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"he has already accepted some new spending cuts","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"and is giving up some of the tax increases","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"he ' s sought .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"\" Take the deal , \"","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"he urged the GOP ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"pointing to his own offer","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"that would raise taxes on those","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"making $ 400,000 or more","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"- already a concession from his preferred $ 250,000 level -","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and would accept slower growth in Social Security benefits ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"but would also add in new unemployment benefits and another round of stimulus spending .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"his plan matches tax increases dollar for dollar with spending cuts ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"though the Republicans disputed that ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"it amounted to $ 1.3 trillion in tax increases with only $ 930 billion in spending cuts .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"\" It is very hard for them to say yes to me , \"","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"the president said .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"\" But at some point , they ' ve got to take me out of it","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"and think about their voters ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and think about what ' s best for the country . \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Both sides left room for further negotiations ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"and Mr. Obama said","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"they are remarkably close on principle","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"now that Mr. Boehner has signaled","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"he is willing to raise tax rates on at least some taxpayers .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"The president said","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"now both sides are just haggling over the right levels of spending cuts and tax increases .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"That makes Thursday ' s vote fraught with peril for Mr. Boehner .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"If Republicans don ' t pass their bill ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"it will leave Mr. Boehner wounded , both with party colleagues and in his negotiations with Mr. Obama .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Conservatives in the House said","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"they can not support any tax rate increase ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"and conservative interest groups said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"they will penalize lawmakers","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"who do vote for Mr. Boehner ' s bill","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"in their year-end scorecards .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Rep. Tim Huelskamp , Kansas Republican , said","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"voting yes would violate his no-new-taxes pledge to his constituents .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" If I went home","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and told them","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"- after taking pledge","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"to not raise taxes -","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"and voted for that ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"I would certainly deserve primary opposition ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and my wife might be the first one","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"to run , \"","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi said","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"the Republicans should not expect Democratic help","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"and doubted","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Mr. Boehner can get his bill through .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"what we saw here earlier was really an act of desperation .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"It didn ' t look like , to me , a person","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"who had the votes , \"","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Republicans were still tweaking the final version of their bill late Wednesday","depth":3},{"id":89,"text":"in order to try to win enough support .","depth":3},{"id":90,"text":"Mr. Boehner says","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"his plan will keep taxes low for 99.8 percent of taxpayers ,","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"and would amount to a $ 3.9 billion tax cut","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"compared with the current law .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"The White House , though , said","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"Mr. Boehner ' s Plan B would amount to a $ 50,000 tax cut for millionaires ,","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"who will still pay lower rates on their income up to $ 1 million .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"White House Communications Director Dan Pfeiffer faulted Mr. Boehner ' s plan for what","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"it left out :","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"It does not extend unemployment benefits ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"it does not end the looming $ 110 billion in spending cuts ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"and it fails to boost payments for doctors","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"who treat Medicare patients .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Republicans said","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"their Plan B was not intended to solve the entire fiscal cliff ,","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"but rather to be a short-term solution","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"to make sure","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"tax rates didn ' t rise for most Americans on Jan. 1 .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":195,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":117,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":115,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":112,"right":114,"relation":"adver